It's an exciting time at AIG. We continue to manage through unprecedented circumstances across the globe, while elevating our market-leading businesses. And we look forward to 2021. I remain confident that our team will continue to execute on our strategies for growth, and we'll separate the life and retirement business from AIG.

So we look forward to updating you on future calls. Have a great day. Thank you very much.

